# PAGI XCURZENS - Cursor rules

- **Project:** PAGI XCURZENS. Use "pagi-xcurzens" / "pagi_xcurzens" / "PAGI XCURZENS" in names and docs. Do not use legacy naming (pagi-uac-main, PAGI-UAC, pagi_uac).
- **Rust:** Crate names are `pagi_xcurzens_core`, `pagi-xcurzens-gateway`. Imports use `pagi_xcurzens_core` (snake_case in code).
- **Gateway:** Single source of truth at `http://127.0.0.1:8000`. UI and scripts talk to the Rust gateway only.
- **Scripts:** PowerShell orchestrator scripts live in repo root; `$ProjectName` and headers are "PAGI XCURZENS"; paths are relative to repo root (pagi-xcurzens folder).
